# HR System - Project Overview

Aplikasi web **Ruby on Rails 7.2** untuk manajemen karyawan, absensi, dan cuti.

## Tech Stack

- **Ruby** 3.3.0
- **Rails** 7.2
- **Database** SQLite (development/test), configurable untuk production
- **Frontend** ERB, Stimulus.js, Turbo, Chart.js, Importmap
- **Assets** Propshaft, Inter font
- **Deployment** Kamal (Docker)

## Struktur Utama

- `app/controllers/` - Dashboard, Employees, Attendances, Leaves, Reports, Search
- `app/models/` - Employee, Attendance, Leave, Activity
- `app/helpers/` - `icon(name)` untuk SVG, `breadcrumbs()`, `format_currency()`, `time_ago_short()`
- `app/javascript/controllers/` - Stimulus: sidebar, dark_mode, animated_counter, chart, toast, search, dropdown, tabs

## Konvensi

- **Bahasa UI**: Indonesia
- **Naming**: snake_case (Ruby), kebab-case (CSS classes)
- **Views**: Gunakan helper `icon(:name)` bukan emoji
